Ivy Manor 2 - Jennifer's Initiation

Heavy rubber bondage, dual whippings, ballet shoe punishment, a giant rubber ball and a honey scene you just shouldn't miss!

Ivy Manor 6 - Pony Girls in Training



Mistress Isabella needs a break, so she phones her friend, Mistress Jean, to see if she can arrange a stay at her pony girl ranch. When the two mistresses get together, their competitive edge takes over. Plenty of hot latex action, unique pony girl outfits and a gorgeous outdoor setting make for an interesting plotline in this sixth edition of the Ivy Manor series.
